 Pat Barton, our Sandbridge Beach real estate specialist, has lived here for the past 30 years when his family first came to Sandbridge in 1958. Whether you're looking for a vacation home or investment property, Pat's knowledge and experience can guide you through the process.  Learn more about Pat Barton, Realtor.
SandbridgeHouses.com features oceanfront homes, bay and waterfront homes and lots and land. Other coverage areas include Lago Mar, Red Mill, Ashville Park, Pungo, and Heritage Park in Virginia Beach. View properties for sale.

 

