Real Estate Capital For Real Business.


Liberty SBF Holdings LLC is a commercial real estate financing company that provides loans to owners and investors of commercial properties. We lend nationwide on a variety of asset types specializing in SBA 504 Loans for company owners, and Bridge Loans and CMBS for property investors. For more information on any of our products and services please call us at (610) 816-0200.






